These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Birthday   | february | december | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, police-officer, lawyer
1. the police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
2. the lawyer is in the middle##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Job   | librarian | lawyer | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, designer, fisherman
1. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fisherman is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Job   | designer | analyst | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, bellflower
1. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Flower   | iris | orchid | bellflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, western, animation
1. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, mango, tomato
1. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
2. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating mango is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Food   | pumpkin | mango | tomato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
