.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel, satire
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | satire | adventure |

